name: CityDAO
description: CityDAO is building a network of assets on chain, starting with a single parcel of land in Wyoming. Each parcel of land is an NFT that can be owned collectively by the DAO collectively or by individuals. It is a DAO, or Decentralized Autonomous Organization, meaning it is managed by the community.
payDisclosure: Every donator has a 3-week cooling-off period for refunds after the fundraising ends. Stay tuned.
